"title": "2360: Jesus Christ, prayers of",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "2360: jesus christ, prayers of",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Prayer was the essence of Jesus Christ's relationship with the Father. He prayed for himself and his mission, and he continues to pray for all believers.</p>\n<h2>Jesus Christ's practice of prayer</h2>\n<h3>He prayed regularly</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke5:16\">LUK 5:16</a></strong> <em>Luke records more instances of Jesus Christ praying than any other Gospel writer.</em></p>\n<h3>He often prayed alone</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark1:35\">MRK 1:35</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt14:23\">MAT 14:23</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark6:46\">MRK 6:46</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke6:12\">LUK 6:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke9:18\">LUK 9:18</a></p>\n<h2>Prayer at specific times in Jesus Christ's life</h2>\n<p>Before his death:\n <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:36-Matt26:46\">MAT 26:36–26:46</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark14:32-Mark14:41\">MRK 14:32–14:41</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke22:39-Luke22:46\">LUK 22:39–22:46</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John17:1-John17:26\">JHN 17:1–17:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt27:46\">MAT 27:46</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark15:34\">MRK 15:34</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke23:34\">LUK 23:34</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke23:46\">LUK 23:46</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke3:21-Luke3:22\">LUK 3:21–3:22</a> <em>at his baptism</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke6:12-Luke6:13\">LUK 6:12–6:13</a> <em>before choosing the apostles</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke9:28-Luke9:29\">LUK 9:28–9:29</a> <em>before his transfiguration</em></p>\n<h2>Characteristics of Jesus Christ's prayers</h2>\n<h3>Communion with his Father</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt6:9\">MAT 6:9</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke11:2\">LUK 11:2</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt11:27\">MAT 11:27</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke10:22\">LUK 10:22</a></p>\n<h3>Submission to his Father</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb5:7\">HEB 5:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt6:10\">MAT 6:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:36\">MAT 26:36</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark14:36\">MRK 14:36</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke22:42\">LUK 22:42</a></p>\n<h3>Giving praise and thanks to his Father</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt11:25-Matt11:26\">MAT 11:25–11:26</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke10:21\">LUK 10:21</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt14:19\">MAT 14:19</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark6:41\">MRK 6:41</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke9:16\">LUK 9:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John6:11\">JHN 6:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt15:36\">MAT 15:36</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark8:6-Mark8:7\">MRK 8:6–8:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:26-Matt26:27\">MAT 26:26–26:27</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark14:22-Mark14:23\">MRK 14:22–14:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke22:17-Luke22:19\">LUK 22:17–22:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor11:24\">1CO 11:24</a> <em>the Lord's Supper</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke24:30\">LUK 24:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John11:41-John11:42\">JHN 11:41–11:42</a></p>\n<h2>The scope of Jesus Christ's prayers</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt19:13-Matt19:15\">MAT 19:13–19:15</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark10:13-Mark10:16\">MRK 10:13–10:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke18:15-Luke18:17\">LUK 18:15–18:17</a> <em>for children</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke22:31-Luke22:32\">LUK 22:31–22:32</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:16\">JHN 14:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John17:6-John17:19\">JHN 17:6–17:19</a>; \n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke23:34\">LUK 23:34</a> <em>for his persecutors</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John12:27-John12:28\">JHN 12:27–12:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John17:1-John17:5\">JHN 17:1–17:5</a>; \n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/John17:20-John17:26\">JHN 17:20–17:26</a> <em>for all believers</em></p>\n<h2>Jesus Christ's continuing ministry of prayer</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb7:25\">HEB 7:25</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:34\">ROM 8:34</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John2:1\">1JN 2:1</a></p>\n<h2>Jesus Christ's teaching about prayer</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt6:9-Matt6:15\">MAT 6:9–6:15</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke11:2-Luke11:4\">LUK 11:2–11:4</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:44\">MAT 5:44</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt6:5-Matt6:8\">MAT 6:5–6:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke6:28\">LUK 6:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke18:1-Luke18:8\">LUK 18:1–18:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke18:9-Luke18:14\">LUK 18:9–18:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke21:36\">LUK 21:36</a></p>",
